data.description: Welcome home to peace and serenity in Brookwood! This wonderful home is waiting for you with a flexible floorplan, soaring ceilings, and tons of windows for an abundance of natural lighting. The open concept kitchen and living area is the perfect space for entertaining family and friends with heated porcelain tile floors, stainless steel appliances, gas cooking, and more! Main floor bedroom with Jr suite that's perfect for out of town guests. Upstairs features your primary suite with private en suite, 3 addl bedrooms, full bath and bamboo flooring throughout all rooms. Escape to your ultra private backyard with gorgeous mature shade trees and concrete patio that's perfect for a BBQ. Community Pool and maturely shaded pathways! Prime Eagle location being just a couple minutes from downtown restaurants, boutiques, parks and much more!
